annotation.text:
[Count Basie & His Orchestra] may or may not be the same as the [Count Basie Orchestra], if you can shed some disambiguation and or links on this matter it would be really appreciated.

Remember though, that the ArtistAnnotation is not the correct forum for discussion, please take this up in the mailinglist, wiki or IRC. thank you
